																		Author Post
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/riemann" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1787775); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1787775&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610204538" alt="Riemann" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1787775)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/riemann" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1787775); return false;" >Riemann</a></span> <span class="odate time_1603478065 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">23 Oct 2020 18:34</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4802518">
									

<p>So after reading <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2893766); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2893766&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1603483092" alt="Croquembouche" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2893766)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2893766); return false;">Croquembouche</a></span>'s sublime <a href="/ambrose-vienna">Ambrose Vienna</a> while being very unsober, I got inspired to write the version that I wanted to see - something a bit less clean cut, more concerned with the implications of <em>something</em> being taken from this reviewer. I also wanted the mental imagery of a pile of profiteroles performing a rendition of Bob Dylan's <em>Hurricane</em>, but that was lost in the editing.</p>
<p>It went through a lot of changes, and largely for the better, leaving us with what I like to think is a cross-section of someone looking back over their life, seeing the cumulative choices that they have made, and being destroyed by it.</p>
<p>A hearty thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2893766); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2893766&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1603483092" alt="Croquembouche" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2893766)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2893766); return false;">Croquembouche</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3440103); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1603483092" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3440103); return false;">Captain Kirby</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1613974); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1613974&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1603483092" alt="UraniumEmpire" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1613974)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1613974); return false;">UraniumEmpire</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gaffsey" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6590029); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6590029&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1603483092" alt="Gaffsey" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6590029)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gaffsey" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6590029); return false;">Gaffsey</a></span> for their feedback on this. And a double thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2893766); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2893766&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1603483092" alt="Croquembouche" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2893766)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2893766); return false;">Croquembouche</a></span> for all his CSS help, without which this article would not be what it is.</p>

