			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4802575">
									

<p>The first half of this is slow but engrossing, it's a nice pace and cadence to see in an article. Initially, I felt it was a bit too slow and meandering, but the second half more than makes up for it; it pays off on that build-up exceptionally well. To a certain extent, I still think it could be a bit more direct, but the strength of the writing makes that feel like an unnecessary nitpick in the grand scheme of things. This is good stuff. +1</p>

