<p>I would say that the first half did a great job of building up the tension, and the second half was good, but maybe a tad too abstracted. I think it needs to be more grounded for it to be as engaging as the first half. Still, the energy and emotion expressed in this piece was phenomenal!</p>
<p>I am looking forward to the Ambrose Renaissance.</p>
<p>+1!</p>

